&quot;A confession of love with your lives on the line...&quot;

A class of 140 students are brought to an Experimental Town, where a being called 1st claims to be they're &quot;tester&quot; and commands them to display true love for the sake of his test. Confessing your love and having it reciprocated means the pair will be able to leave, but failure means death.

[b]Note:[/b] Originally serialized digitally through Jump+. Only the first three collections were published physically and all later releases were digital exclusives.

Lacile is a boy who lives in the mountains with his grandfather and dreams of seeing the world. One day while checking traps in the woods he comes across the runaway Princess Leana who shares the same dream. Together they set out to explore the world.
